# /etc/postfix/virtual — virtual alias map
# Maps envelope recipient addresses to local delivery targets.
#
# Format: recipient@domain  destination
#
# Generate hash: postmap /etc/postfix/virtual
#
# Add a line per user. Example:
#   alice@example.com   alice@example.com
#   bob@example.com     bob@example.com
#   postmaster@example.com  alice@example.com
#
# ── Catch-all (comment out if not wanted) ─────────────────────
# @example.com  postmaster@example.com
